<paragraph base="SL33296" principles="no" id="IAS39_93"><paranum>93</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IAS 39"/><data name="paranum" value="93"/></prolog><body><p id="IAS39_P0615">When an unrecognised <xref base="SL134655" href="IAS39_9_hedge-accounting.dita#IAS39_9_hedge-accounting/IAS39_P0208" scope="local">firm commitment<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0131"/></ph></xref> is designated as a <xref base="SL134658" href="IAS39_9_hedge-accounting.dita#IAS39_9_hedge-accounting/IAS39_P0211">hedged item<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0166"/></ph></xref>, the subsequent cumulative change in the <xref base="SL134652" href="../ifrs13/IFRS13_APPA.dita#IFRS13_APPA/IFRS13_DI0006" scope="local">fair value<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0118"/></ph></xref> of the firm commitment attributable to the hedged risk is recognised as an asset or liability with a corresponding gain or loss recognised in profit or loss (see <xref base="F19328335" href="IAS39_89.dita#IAS39_89/IAS39_89_V2" id="IAS39_X0561">paragraph 89(b)</xref>). The changes in the fair value of the <xref base="SL134657" href="IAS39_9_hedge-accounting.dita#IAS39_9_hedge-accounting/IAS39_P0210" scope="local">hedging instrument<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0167"/></ph></xref> are also recognised in profit or loss.</p></body></paragraph>